vaccineProgram.screenHeader: These appointments are ONLY for City of New York employees who are in roles covered by phases 1a and 1b. You will be asked to provide your City employee ID or a letter from your supervisor confirming your employment status when you get to the vaccination site. These City employee appointments are for Queens and Staten Island vaccine sites only. If you are a City employee and looking for appointments in the Bronx, Brooklyn, or Manhattan visit https://somosvaccinations.com by copying and pasting the link into your browser.
vaccineProgram.description: NYC Employees: employees employed by NYC (excluding FDNY) eligible under Phase 1A and 1B priority groups. Eligible NYC Employees can also sign up in the General Public program.
